API docs by Redocly

WPPConnect API REST (1.1.0)

Download OpenAPI specification:Download

Auth

generate-token (Gera token Bearer para sessão)

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
secretkey
required
string
Example: THISISMYSECURETOKEN

(Required) chave do admin

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/{secretkey}/generate-token

Response samples

  • 201
Content type
application/json
{
  • "status": "Success",
  • "session": "nova",
  • "token": "$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS",
  • "full": "nova:$2b$10$N9xrdqCW4S1jpNyB44L1nuXj79EAvo83MS6uxhBg8JOvWNLV8QlaS"
}

start-session (Retorna QRCode de login)

Inicializa a sessão

Authorizations:
httpBearer
Request Body schema: application/json
webhook
required
string

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/start-session

Request samples

  • Payload
Content type
application/json
{
  • "webhook": "https://webhook.site/7cc2944d-3967-4cea-988c-d57ea80bce5f"
}

status-session (Atualiza QRCode de login)

Retorna o status da session

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/status-session

qrcode-session (Pegar qrCode de autenticação via stream)

Retorna o status da session

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/qrcode-session

check-connection-session (status da conexão)

Verifica se a sessáo esta conectada

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/check-connection-session

close-session

finaliza a sessão

Authorizations:
httpBearer

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/close-session

Chat

Chat Methods

All Chats

Retrieves all chats

Authorizations:
httpBearer
header Parameters
Content-Type
required
string
Example: application/json

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/all-chats

Chat By Id

Retrieves chat object of given contact id

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
phone
required
string
Example: 556593077171

Phone without @c.us

query Parameters
isGroup
required
string
Example:

Indicate that phone id given is group or not

header Parameters
Content-Type
required
string
Example: application/json

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/chat-by-id/{phone}

Get messages in Chat

Get messages in chat.

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
phone
required
string

The contact ID, with @c.us or @g.us

query Parameters
count
integer
Example:

Quantity of messages. Specify -1 to get everything (may take a long time).

id
string
Example:

Get messages after/before this message ID.

direction
string
Example:

Specify the direction in which the messages are gonna be retrieved. If present, must be 'after' or 'before'

header Parameters
Content-Type
required
string
Example: application/json

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/get-messages/{phone}

Get Media Data

Retrieves Base64 data media and mimetype

Authorizations:
httpBearer
path Parameters
msgId
required
string
Example: true_62895808067171@c.us_3EB07058C5DEACB799EB

The message id

header Parameters
Content-Type
required
string
Example: application/json

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/get-media-by-message/{msgId}

Send Reply

Envia um arquivo para um número de telefone.

Authorizations:
httpBearer
Request Body schema: application/json
phone
required
string
message
required
string
messageId
required
string
isGroup
required
boolean

Responses

http://localhost:21465/api/{session}/send-reply

Request samples

  • Payload
Content type
application/json
{
  • "phone": "554498005216",
  • "message": "mensagem de resposta",
  • "messageId": "1",
  • "isGroup": false
}
